StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_GetASVABExamData]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@MarineCandidateId int, @Version varchar(3), @ASVABDate date.me AS
SELECT CONVERT(VARCHAR, ASVAB_DATE, 106) AS EXAM_DATE, 'ASVAB' AS EXAM_TYPE, VERSION, AFQT_SCORE, GS_SUBTEST, AR_SUBTEST, WK_SUBTEST, PC_SUBTEST, NO_SUBTEST, CS_SUBTEST, AS_SUBTEST, MK_SUBTEST, MC_SUBTEST, EI_SUBTEST, VE_SUBTEST, GT_SCORE, EL_SCORE, CL_SCORE, MM_SCORE, MEPS_ORGANIZATION_ID FROM CANDIDATE_ASVAB Where MARINE_CANDIDATE_ID = @MarineCandidateID AND VERSION = @Version AND ASVAB_DATE = @ASVABDate
